@startuml
title SSD - Set Up Recruitment Process

actor Custom Manager

Custom Manager -> ":System": Request to set up a recruitment process
":System" --> Custom Manager: Displays list of job openings
Custom Manager -> ":System": Selects a job opening
":System" --> Custom Manager: Asks for details of each recruitment phase
Custom Manager -> ":System": Provides phase details
":System" --> Custom Manager: Confirms details and asks for confirmation
Custom Manager -> ":System": Confirms setup
":System" --> Custom Manager: Confirms recruitment process setup

@enduml
